data.title: About: Judy Dickinson
data.meta_description: Judy Dickinson (born March 4, 1950) is an American professional golfer who played on the LPGA Tour. She competed as Judy Clark from 1978 until her marriage to PGA Tour golfer Gardner Dickinson in late 1985. Dickinson won four times on the LPGA Tour between 1985 and 1992. Dickinson served as president of the LPGA from 1990 to 1992.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

جودي ديكنسون (بالإنجليزية: Judy Dickinson)‏ هي لاعبة غولف أمريكية، ولدت في 4 مارس 1950 في آكرون في الولايات المتحدة. (ar)

Judy Dickinson (born March 4, 1950) is an American professional golfer who played on the LPGA Tour. She competed as Judy Clark from 1978 until her marriage to PGA Tour golfer Gardner Dickinson in late 1985. Dickinson won four times on the LPGA Tour between 1985 and 1992. Dickinson served as president of the LPGA from 1990 to 1992. (en)

Judy Dickinson (nascida em 4 de março de 1950) é uma jogadora norte-americana de golfe profissional que atualmente joga nos torneios do circuito LPGA. Competiu sob o nome de Judy Clark, de 1978 até o seu casamento com o jogador de golfe do PGA Tour, , no final de 1985. Dickinson venceu quatro vezes no LPGA Tour entre 1985 e 1992 e atuou como presidente do LPGA entre 1990 e 1992. (pt)
